  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dba \u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The stolen cab is traced through Facebook",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Nittambune reports that a cab that had been stolen on the 21st while parked on the road in front of Kurunegala Maliyadeva College was found again within three days through a Facebook post.",
        "The cab was found this morning (25th) while it was parked in Nittambuwa city.",
        "Mr. Ananda Gunawardena, a resident of Kurunegala, is the owner of this red Mitsubishi cab worth about 40 lakh rupees. Mr. A came with his wife and went to watch a sports match in Maliadeva College. Someone stole this cab which was parked in front of the college.",
        "On checking the CCTV camera systems installed on the main roads of Kurunegala city, it was recorded that someone was driving the vehicle on the Negombo road.",
        "Mr. Sisira Valisinghe, who works in the X-ray treatment department of Kurunegala Teaching Hospital, saw a post posted by Mr. Gunawardena on his Facebook page and displayed the same post on his Facebook page asking for help in finding the missing cab.",
        "A friend of Mr. Valisingha who had seen that post saw the stolen cab parked near the Colombo road in Nittambuwa town this morning and immediately informed Mr. Valisingha about it and then informed the owner and informed the Nittambuwa police and proceeded to take the cab into police custody.",
        "The Nittambuwa Police are conducting further investigations as to whether the person who took the stolen cab had left it or had parked it and gone on another business."
      ],
